defaultUnder the current proposals, customers living in temporary accommodation owned by the local authority are not exempt from the social sector size criteria, although those in most other types of
default temporary accommodation are.
default6.2
default              
defaultKnowsley Council are currently developing a dispersed model of temporary 
defaultaccommodation. Properties will at time be under occupied in line with the size criteria and therefore result in a short fall for the occupier, who ar
defaulte benefit dependent and would not have the means to meet the shortfall
