defaultAuthorities could consider commissioning a
defaultdditional exempt accommodation to use as temporary accommodation.  Given that budgets for 2013-14 have now been set, this would not be viable without grant funding from DCLG.  In addition, under the current proposals for social size criteria and benefit ca
